dct_alternative_sm: Formosa Strait to Yangtze River entrance (Amoy to Shanghai)
dct_description_sm: From British, Japanese and Chinese surveys to 1935 ; published Feb. 1938, at the Hydrographic Office, under the authority of the Secretary of the Navy.
Depths shown by soundings and tints; relief by form lines and spot heights.
"Current diagrams" note, buoy legend, variation lines, locations of larger scale charts.
Shows low water areas, islands, waterways, lights/visibility, towns, railroads (including "under construction").
